statements: SELECT * FROM real_estate_investment_returns;
SELECT property_name, purchase_price, sale_price FROM real_estate_investment_returns ORDER BY purchase_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, return_on_investment FROM real_estate_investment_returns WHERE return_on_investment > 0 ORDER BY return_on_investment DESC;
SELECT AVG(return_on_investment) AS avg_roi FROM real_estate_investment_returns WHERE property_type = 'Residential';
SELECT property_name, market_performance_analysis FROM real_estate_investment_returns WHERE market_performance_analysis LIKE '%positive%' ORDER BY sale_date ASC;
SELECT property_name, property_type, purchase_price, sale_price FROM real_estate_investment_returns;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_investment_returns WHERE purchase_price > 500000 AND return_on_investment > 0.1;
SELECT investment_id, property_name, purchase_date, sale_date, return_on_investment FROM real_estate_investment_returns WHERE purchase_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_name, sale_price, market_performance_analysis FROM real_estate_investment_returns ORDER BY sale_price DESC;
SELECT AVG(return_on_investment) AS average_roi, MAX(purchase_price) AS max_purchase_price FROM real_estate_investment_returns GROUP BY property_type ORDER BY average_roi DESC;

SELECT property_id, property_address, purchase_price FROM real_estate_properties WHERE property_type = 'Apartment' AND annual_rental_income > 20000;

SELECT P.property_id, P.property_address, IR.total_return FROM real_estate_properties AS P JOIN investment_returns AS IR ON P.property_id = IR.property_id WHERE IR.ROI > 0.1;
